<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
     SECTION 2: WHY THIS AREA
════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2ead4); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#b98229; margin-bottom:1rem;">Local Expertise</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#191817; margin-bottom:1.75rem;">Strong value positioning on the inner south corridor.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Fairfield sits about four kilometres south of the CBD in Brisbane's inner south, bordered by Annerley to the east and Yeronga to the south-west. It is a family suburb with a distinct character: tree-lined streets, predominantly pre-war and post-war timber homes, and a consistent owner-occupier base that gives the suburb a quiet, settled feel. The suburb's value positioning relative to Dutton Park and Annerley makes it attractive to buyers who want inner south proximity and character stock without paying those suburbs' premiums.
    </p>
<!-- APPRAISAL FORM -->
<div style="background:#fff; border-left:4px solid #b98229; padding:2rem 2rem 1.75rem; margin:2rem 0; border-radius:16px;">
  <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.72rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.18em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#b98229; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Free Appraisal</p>
  <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.4rem; font-weight:300; color:#191817; margin-bottom:1.25rem; line-height:1.25;">Find out what your Fairfield home is worth.</h3>
  <form method="POST" action="https://formspree.io/f/xnjgedwp" style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0.75rem;">
  <input type="text" name="_gotcha" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" style="display:none" />
    <input type="hidden" name="_next" value="https://danielgierach.com/thank-you?from=suburb-appraisal" />
    <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="Appraisal enquiry: Fairfield" />
    <input type="hidden" name="_source" value="fairfield" />
    <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:0.75rem;" class="suburb-form-grid">
      <input type="text" name="name" required placeholder="Your name" autocomplete="name"
        style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.88rem; padding:0.7rem 0.9rem; border:1px solid rgba(28,25,23,0.18); background:#faf9f7; color:#191817; outline:none; width:100%; box-sizing:border-box;" />
      <input type="email" name="email" required placeholder="Email address" autocomplete="email"
        style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.88rem; padding:0.7rem 0.9rem; border:1px solid rgba(28,25,23,0.18); background:#faf9f7; color:#191817; outline:none; width:100%; box-sizing:border-box;" />
    </div>
    <input type="text" name="property_address" required placeholder="Your Fairfield address (street + number)"
      style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.88rem; padding:0.7rem 0.9rem; border:1px solid rgba(28,25,23,0.18); background:#faf9f7; color:#191817; outline:none; width:100%; box-sizing:border-box;" />
    <div style="display:flex; gap:0.75rem; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <button type="submit"
        style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.78rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; background:#b98229; color:#191817; padding:0.75rem 1.75rem; border:none; cursor:pointer; white-space:nowrap;border-radius:8px;">
        Request My Free Appraisal
      </button>
      <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:300; color:#78716c; margin:0; line-height:1.5;">Daniel will be in touch promptly. No pressure.</p>
    </div>
  </form>
</div>
<style>
  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .suburb-form-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
  }
</style>
<!-- END APPRAISAL FORM -->
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      I cover the inner south corridor regularly and understand how Fairfield sits in relation to the neighbouring suburbs. Buyers who arrive here have often been searching Dutton Park and Annerley and found themselves priced out, or they specifically targeted Fairfield because they identified the value gap and made a deliberate decision. Both buyer types are active and motivated, which is a good starting point for a well-run campaign.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Fairfield Gardens and the network of tree-lined streets give the suburb an amenity story that photographs well and resonates with family buyers during inspections. The Fairfield station on the Beenleigh line provides a direct rail link to the CBD, which matters to the professional buyer segment. PA Hospital and Griffith University are both accessible, supporting a rental market that attracts investment buyers at the lower end of the price range. Character homes on the quieter streets away from Ipswich Road attract the strongest competition, with buyers comparing Fairfield directly against Annerley and the Yeronga corridor to its south.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229; border-radius:16px;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Fairfield Specialist</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Inner South Brisbane</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229; border-radius:16px;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Family Character</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Strong value relative to inner south neighbours</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/annerley" style="color:#b98229;">Annerley</a>, <a href="/suburbs/yeronga" style="color:#b98229;">Yeronga</a>, <a href="/suburbs/dutton-park" style="color:#b98229;">Dutton Park</a>, <a href="/suburbs/greenslopes" style="color:#b98229;">Greenslopes</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

